ByNameStored - Interface in fi.helsinki.cs.turridevelop.util
A class implements the ByNameStored interface to indicate that it only changes its name when it has tested that all ByNameContainers registered to the instance do not already have element with the same name by calling their 'has' methods and after a successful change notifies them by calling their 'nameChanged' methods.
